#

Cheesy Quesadilla

15 min
$5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free Option

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Tags:

QuickEasyComfort Food

Description

A quick and delicious cheesy quesadilla, perfect for a satisfying snack or meal!

Ingredients

  • flour tortillas: 2
  • shredded cheese (cheddar or monterey jack): 1 cup
  • cooked chicken (optional): 1/2 cup
  • salsa: to taste
  • cooking oil or butter: 1 tablespoon
